                <p>We are bringing together a <span class="cli-highlight">global team</span> to tackle a global challenge.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cli-row" style="padding-top: 3em">
            <p class="cli-text">Follow our journey on our <a class="cactus-link" href="/blog">blog</a>, with our <a class="cactus-link" href="#">newsletter</a>, or <a class="cactus-link" href="#">contact us</a>.</p>
